# ============================================================
# Globe AMS — 05. Appointment Lifecycle
# ============================================================
# Full lifecycle: Create (Pending) → Confirm → Complete
#                                  └→ Cancel
#
# Prerequisites (fill IDs from previous files):
#   @globeAdminToken  — from 01_admin-auth.http
#   @globeTenantId    — from 01_admin-auth.http login response
#   @globeServiceId   — from 04_services.http step 1
#   @globeStaffId     — AppUser.Id of a staff member in globe tenant
#                       (use the admin's AppUser.Id for initial tests)
#
# Note on staffId: the admin's AppUser.Id is in the login response as "userId".
# Use that as staffId for the first test — in production, you'd have dedicated Staff records.
# ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5006

@globeAdminToken = PASTE_GLOBE_ADMIN_JWT_HERE
@globeTenantId   = PASTE_GLOBE_TENANT_ID_HERE
@globeServiceId  = PASTE_GLOBE_SERVICE_ID_HERE  # from 04_services.http
@globeStaffId    = PASTE_GLOBE_STAFF_APPUSER_ID_HERE  # "userId" from login response

# Filled after creation:
@appointmentId1  = PASTE_AFTER_CREATE_STEP_1
@appointmentId2  = PASTE_AFTER_CREATE_STEP_7

# Client token (from 03_register-verify-login.http step 4):
@clientToken     = PASTE_CLIENT_JWT_HERE

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 1. Create appointment — Pending status
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# @name createAppointment1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{globeAdminToken}}

{
  "serviceId": "{{globeServiceId}}",
  "staffId": "{{globeStaffId}}",
  "startTime": "2026-06-10T10:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Integration test appointment #1"
}

###
# ✅ Expected 201:
# {
#   "id": "<appt-guid>",       ← set as @appointmentId1
#   "tenantId": "<globe-guid>",← sourced from JWT, not body
#   "status": "Pending",
#   "serviceId": "...",
#   "staffId": "...",
#   "startTime": "2026-06-10T10:00:00Z",
#   "notes": "Integration test appointment #1"
# }
# ✓ TenantId = globe (from JWT), Pending status on creation

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 2. Get all appointments for Globe tenant
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/tenant/{{globeTenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{globeAdminToken}}

###
# ✅ Expected 200 — array containing the appointment just created

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 3. Get appointment by ID
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId1}}
Authorization: Bearer {{globeAdminToken}}

###
# ✅ Expected 200 — appointment detail with status = "Pending"

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 4. Confirm appointment (TenantAdmin / Staff role)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId1}}/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{globeAdminToken}}

###
# ✅ Expected 204 No Content — status transitions to "Confirmed"

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 5. Verify status is Confirmed
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId1}}
Authorization: Bearer {{globeAdminToken}}

###
# ✅ Expected 200 — status = "Confirmed"

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 6. Complete appointment (TenantAdmin / Staff role)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId1}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{globeAdminToken}}

###
# ✅ Expected 204 No Content — status transitions to "Completed"

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 7. Create second appointment (for cancel test)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# @name createAppointment2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{globeAdminToken}}

{
  "serviceId": "{{globeServiceId}}",
  "staffId": "{{globeStaffId}}",
  "startTime": "2026-06-11T14:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Appointment to be cancelled"
}

###
# ✅ Expected 201 — copy id to @appointmentId2

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 8. Cancel appointment (any authenticated user)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId2}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{globeAdminToken}}

"Customer requested cancellation — schedule conflict"

###
# ✅ Expected 204 No Content — status transitions to "Cancelled"

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 9. Verify appointment is Cancelled
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId2}}
Authorization: Bearer {{globeAdminToken}}

###
# ✅ Expected 200 — status = "Cancelled", cancellationReason present

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 10. Create appointment without auth (expect 401)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceId": "{{globeServiceId}}",
  "staffId": "{{globeStaffId}}",
  "startTime": "2026-06-12T09:00:00Z"
}

###
# ❌ Expected 401 Unauthorized — [Authorize] on controller

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 11. Confirm with Client role (expect 403)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId1}}/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

###
# ❌ Expected 403 Forbidden — [Authorize(Roles = "TenantAdmin,Staff")]

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 12. Complete with Client role (expect 403)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId1}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

###
# ❌ Expected 403 Forbidden

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 13. Get appointment by ID without auth (expect 401)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/{{appointmentId1}}

###
# ❌ Expected 401 Unauthorized
